# Preface
Hey! You've found this page by either looking through this repository or when you when to submit an issue, you saw the banner notification telling you to come here. Either way, please follow these "rules" to the best of your ability. *This exists so that we can have consistency throughout all issues so everything is organized.*

# How To Submit An Issue
- Be as clear as possible, explain whatever you're trying to convey as if we're all 5 years old
- If you're submitting a bug report, be extremely detailed. Tell us how we can reproduce the bug so that it can be fixed
- **[USE THE CORRECT LABELS](https://github.com/acidflip/rScanner/labels)**
